    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For Your hand stopping I’d almost implore,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When I feel I cannot take any more."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet You are God! Oh, how can You give way?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Please, Lord, do not give in; wait ’til I obey."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My eyes are teary; I can’t see You clearly,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As though all Your words aren’t as real as before."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You make me decrease, that You might thus increase,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To make Your will sweeter than e’er before."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If Your good pleasure and will should decree"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That I must take suff’ring’s yoke upon me,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then may my heart’s deepest joy be this thing—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Obeying Your will to take the suffering."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
