        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Therefore I’d welcome Your hindering pull,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If thus I could cause Your heart to be joyful."
            }
